Escape (https://www.portmaster.games) 
=========================

Original version by:
escape.spacebar.org

Portmaster Version: 	

- Cebion https://github.com/Cebion
	
Description 
===========
Escape is a fun puzzle game in the tradition of Adventures of Lolo or Chip's Challenge 
Unlike either of those games, Escape doesn't rely at all on reflexesâ€”it's all about your brain.


To compile:
===========
svn checkout https://svn.code.sf.net/p/tom7misc/svn/trunk tom7misc-svn
cd tom7misc/cc-tools
g++ -c -march=native -Wall -I. --std=c++2a -O3 -Wno-psabi util.cc -o util.o
cd ../escapex
export LINUX=true
make
strip escape.exe

 
Controls:
=============

Start		= Start Game / Restart Level
DPAD		= Move
A			= Enter
B			= Undo
Y			= Bookmarks